CAPE TOWN - Police are searching for four armed men who robbed a social grant payout point at the Eikestad Mall in Stellenbosch on Tuesday. "An undisclosed amount of cash was taken. An armed robbery case is under investigation," Western Cape police spokewoman Noloyiso Rwexana said in a statement. No further details were given. Police are urging members of the public to come forward with information that could lead to the gunmen. African News Agency